column2: Had to be a woman hahaha
Tday afternoon, my mom txted me askin for help fixin a machine or smth
So I went n sent the money to the acc she gave me… but guess what???
I posted abt it on my profile
N then these two came to roast me for fallin for it
Looks like they got nothing better to do than make fun of people who actually need help. Kinda sad!
After falling for a scam, she’s still gonna listen to another girl
But is that even a girl? I’ve seen monsters prettier than that lol
